    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this Fire Boy demo, you'll be able to explore the first 3 levels with 70% of the content unlocked in each one. Face enemies, help the hero take his first steps on this journey, and get a taste of the epic adventure awaiting you in the full version. Discover Fire Boy’s initial powers and get ready for the challenges ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/525a54a2d72069b4b84e7d451555f5dc.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/525a54a2d72069b4b84e7d451555f5dc.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/525a54a2d72069b4b84e7d451555f5dc.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its comedic personality allows for funny interactions, especially when failing or succeeding in unexpected ways. It has unique lines for different situations, such as losing a life or gaining a new ability, but these dialogues may vary depending on the player's actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/633dfd159c51cd380ae392f7dde1b63a.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/633dfd159c51cd380ae392f7dde1b63a.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/633dfd159c51cd380ae392f7dde1b63a.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These lines will make you laugh out loud and moments that will warm your heart, this game promises to be a memorable adventure from start to finish. Put your skills to the test. Join the <strong>Fire Boy</strong> on his epic mission and &quot;Step into the Heat of Adventure. Destiny Calls!&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/a62e792ae8ea60052e95424d3cbf4a2a.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/a62e792ae8ea60052e95424d3cbf4a2a.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/a62e792ae8ea60052e95424d3cbf4a2a.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Summary of the ''brief summary'' of the story...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On an ordinary day, Aldo finds a magic sphere, triggering an interplanetary journey. He teams up with Guto, an alien who seeks him out for help to save dinosaur eggs that were stolen by the Monstrengos and also to recover the Silver Fire Armor (it enhances his Fire Power), thus becoming the legendary Fire Warrior. With the clock ticking against him, he faces a race against time. As the seconds pass, the eggs are on the verge of hatching, and the Monstrengos are lurking, ready to turn the eggs into snacks or enslave the future dinosaur hatchlings. Aldo embarks on a heroic mission, determined to rescue the eggs and prevent a terrible fate at the hands of the enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/754affc02fbdf8a4a115892709230f2e.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/754affc02fbdf8a4a115892709230f2e.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/754affc02fbdf8a4a115892709230f2e.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now I want to share with you a little more about the biggest dream of my life: to create a game that goes beyond entertainment, a game that is a unique, exciting, and memorable experience. This dream came to life in &quot;Fire Boy.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/05c4f375f33ca6f740967d1a900be95b.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/05c4f375f33ca6f740967d1a900be95b.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/05c4f375f33ca6f740967d1a900be95b.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since childhood, games have always been more than just fun for me. They were gateways to incredible worlds, captivating stories, and unforgettable characters. I hope I can provide that same magic for others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/71c0a801e520b69d788064b1d6640774.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/71c0a801e520b69d788064b1d6640774.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/71c0a801e520b69d788064b1d6640774.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>&quot;Fire Boy&quot;</strong> is not just a game. It is the materialization of years of passion, creativity, and hard work. It is the story of a companion and friend hero, who faces great challenges in a world full of dangers and mysteries, who needs your help. It is an adventure that will take you to places you never imagined, awakening emotions ranging from adrenaline to tenderness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/a49352f83e8c59379b85bb8c35c7b921.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/a49352f83e8c59379b85bb8c35c7b921.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/a49352f83e8c59379b85bb8c35c7b921.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is not just a project or a professional goal, it is the purpose of my life. Every element of the game, from the plot to the gameplay and graphics, is infused with my essence, my experiences, and my unwavering dedication. This game is an extension of myself, a legacy I want to leave to the world of video games. This project encapsulates my creative soul, and that is why every detail is treated with the utmost care and love. The <strong>&quot;Fire Boy&quot;</strong> is born from genuine passion and the desire to create something memorable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/bb8440219285bab97bb459612fa8a3e6.poster.avif?t=1768413430\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/bb8440219285bab97bb459612fa8a3e6.webm?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286980/extras/bb8440219285bab97bb459612fa8a3e6.mp4?t=1768413430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developing a video game is embarking on a journey full of challenges, learning, and above all, passion. Not to mention the boundless dedication! I dedicated myself to creating something truly special, I hope <strong>&quot;Fire Boy&quot;</strong> manages to touch the hearts of everyone who plays it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game made with much love in my humble home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything you see here today was once a dream!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I thank you from the bottom of my heart,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aldo (Caraca Games)</p>",
